promqlQuery.value: pg_stat_activity_count{datname=~"{{datname}}", instance=~"{{instance}}", state=~"idle|idle in transaction|idle in transaction (aborted)"}

dataprimeQuery.text:
source spans
| filter $d.tags['db.statement'] != null
| filter $m.duration != null 
| filter $d.tags['db.system'] == 'postgresql' 
| groupby $d.tags['db.statement'] as $d['tags.db.statement'] agg avg($m.duration) as $d['AVG(ms)']
